# D{{N}} — Actor-Context Interaction Matrix

**Audience:** Stakeholder + Architect (who-touches-what conversations).
**When to look at this:** Onboarding new team members, scoping integrations, identifying actors who span too many contexts (BC-boundary smell).
**Prose gap closed:** `2-event-storm.md` lists actors and the canvases describe inbound/outbound channels per BC; this matrix shows the **N×M intersection** in one frame.

