## Legend

| Symbol | Meaning |
|--------|---------|
| Yellow node | Human actor (role-based, not individual users) |
| Blue node | Internal system (cron, batch, internal services) |
| Pink node | External partner / system (third party) |
| `<==>` edge | Bidirectional `RW` interaction |
| `R` | Actor reads BC state but does not modify it |
| `W` | Actor sends commands/events into BC; does not read back |
| `RW` | Both directions; operationally coupled |
| `—` | No interaction in current model |

**Totals:** {{ACTOR_COUNT}} actors × {{BC_COUNT}} BCs

